author: Dave Williams Bureau Chief Capitol Beat News Service
title: Students from 8 Fulton Schools Qualify for Private School Vouchers
text:
The Governor's Office of Student Achievement has released a list of low-performing schools in Georgia whose students qualify to receive private-school vouchers.
Students from 8 Fulton Schools Qualify for Private School Vouchers
- Dave Williams Bureau Chief Capitol Beat News Service
